flowchart LR
  Browser --> NextUI[Next.js page/component]
  NextUI --> ApiClient[frontend/lib/api.ts]
  ApiClient --> Gateway[NGINX]

  Gateway --> DomainSvc[Target Service Route]
  DomainSvc --> AuthCheck[Token verification via user-service]
  DomainSvc --> DataStore[(Postgres/Mongo)]
  DomainSvc --> AnalyticsEmit[POST /api/analytics/events]

  AnalyticsEmit --> AnalyticsSvc[analytics-service]
  AnalyticsSvc --> EventLog[(events collection)]
  AnalyticsSvc --> ReadModel[(analytics collection)]

  DomainSvc --> Gateway
  Gateway --> NextUI
  NextUI --> Browser
